    -- this will likely fail
    -- let's try `norm_num` on the goal `g "hello" ≠ fun x => pure Syntax.missing`
    -- this will likely fail
    -- let's try `native_decide` on the goal `g "hello" ≠ fun x => pure Syntax.missing`
    -- this should work if the goal is decidable
